title: The Real Housewives of Durban
overview: Welcome to South Africa's West Coast, where the sea nestles up to golden sands and the breeze is coated in warm mist. The sun is shining bright, the 6 rich ladies of The Real Housewives of Durbanv are dressed in their classiest gowns, and they're ready to spill the tea, throw the shade and go to town on our TVs.
